      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ART SESSION (1) sat handy last start at Northam and got the job done by 0.7L at Northam and this looks to shape favourably for Nitika Riordan. Should be up front from the outset and he rates highly on the back of his last start win. Can fire again. DANCEWITHME (4) got the job done two back before a 3.2L defeat most recently over 1200m. The inside draw should help her and it's worth noting she was a $1.70 favourite here two back. Wouldn't surprise to see her get back to winning ways. CHIPILLY (6) is better than she showed last time out when missing by 2.7L at this track and trip 49 days ago. She started her campaign like a house on fire and the stable have hit the reset button with her. Faithfull reunites now and she can bounce back to her best. DOOR BUSTER (5) can bounce back to her best coming back to this trip. LAVISH CHARM (2) disappointed as an odds-on pop last time and is obviously better than that. Can return to form.",
